@ustcweizhou 
Hi, 
I have made the suggested changes, Can you please review?.

@rafaelweingartner 
It is a community thing any one who has bandwidth can pick it up. I do not think this pr will cause any issues, all of the alert messages which we have are far less than 999 characters. If we want to be paranoid and think if some thing can happen, the worse that can happen is the messages in the alter table will be truncated, i think this is still better than not seeing the alert messages at all. Currently the user sees that a particular host is in alert but dose not see any message or the reason for why it went into alert. This PR fixes that issue. So in my opinion it is a improvement from what we have and It dose not cause any issues.

-
